<tr class="">
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; padding-bottom:0.5em;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Einstein_1921_by_F_Schmutzer.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/66/Einstein_1921_by_F_Schmutzer.jpg/220px-Einstein_1921_by_F_Schmutzer.jpg" width="220" height="289" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/66/Einstein_1921_by_F_Schmutzer.jpg/330px-Einstein_1921_by_F_Schmutzer.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/66/Einstein_1921_by_F_Schmutzer.jpg/440px-Einstein_1921_by_F_Schmutzer.jpg 2x" /></a><br />
<span style="">Albert Einstein in 1921</span></td>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<th scope="row" style="text-align:left; background:transparent; line-height:1.1em;">Born</th>
<td class="" style="line-height:1.3em; vertical-align:middle;"><span style="display:none">(<span class="bday">1879-03-14</span>)</span>14 March 1879<br />
<a href="Ulm" title="Ulm">Ulm</a>, <a href="Kingdom_of_W%C3%BCrttemberg" title="Kingdom of Württemberg">Kingdom of Württemberg</a>, <a href="German_Empire" title="German Empire">German Empire</a></td>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<th scope="row" style="text-align:left; background:transparent; line-height:1.1em;">Died</th>
<td class="" style="line-height:1.3em; vertical-align:middle;">18 April 1955<span style="display:none">(<span class="dday deathdate">1955-04-18</span>)</span> (aged&#160;76)<br />
<a href="Princeton,_New_Jersey" title="Princeton, New Jersey">Princeton, New Jersey</a>, United States</td>
</tr>
<tr class="">
