<li><a href="William_Lawrence_Bragg" title="William Lawrence Bragg">W. L. Bragg</a> / <a href="William_Henry_Bragg" title="William Henry Bragg">W. H. Bragg</a> (1915)</li>
<li><a href="Charles_Glover_Barkla" title="Charles Glover Barkla">Barkla</a> (1917)</li>
